            <title>[FLINK-3242] User-specified StateBackend is not Respected if Checkpointing is Disabled</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3242</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In &lt;tt&gt;StreamingJobGraphGenerator.java&lt;/tt&gt; (line 281) the StateBackend is only set on the &lt;tt&gt;StreamConfig&lt;/tt&gt; if checkpointing is enabled.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is easy to fix but we also need to add test to prevent this from happening in the future.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
